scripts.build: echo Build... & rmdir /s /q build 2>nul & mkdir build & xcopy /E /I /Y dist-app build >nul & xcopy /E /I /Y js build\js >nul & xcopy /E /I /Y img build\img >nul & xcopy /E /I /Y css build\css >nul & if exist panel.html copy /Y panel.html build\panel.html >nul & if exist support.html copy /Y support.html build\support.html >nul & if exist yetki-yok.html copy /Y yetki-yok.html build\yetki-yok.html >nul
